OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1772216417
OL,3,CMan and woman arrested over 'murder
OL,4,Cplot' after anti-terror raid
OL,6,FA man and a woman have been arrested
OL,7,Fover a suspected murder plot after a
OL,8,F"pre-planned" counter-terrorism
OL,9,Foperation in Hull.
OL,11,FThe pair, both aged 23, were taken in
OL,12,Ffor questioning on suspicion of
OL,13,Fconspiracy to murder following the
OL,14,Foperation Morpeth Street. The man was
OL,15,Falso arrested on suspicion of
OL,16,Fpossession of a weapon.
OL,18,FBomb disposal experts were called and
OL,19,Fsearches at a property in Hull
OL,20,Fremained ongoing on Thursday afternoon.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
