CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1772216417
OL,3,CMan and woman arrested over 'murder
OL,4,Cplot' after anti-terror raid
OL,6,FPolice have released no further
OL,7,Fdetails about the allegations.
OL,9,FA spokesperson for Counter Terrorism
OL,10,FPolicing North East said: "We
OL,11,Funderstand that local community may
OL,12,Fhave concerns as a result of this
OL,13,Factivity. We would like to reassure
OL,14,Fthem that this arrest is pre-planned
OL,15,Fand intelligence led and there is not
OL,16,Fbelieved to be any immediate risk to
OL,17,Fthe local community.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/3
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
