FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1772216417
OL,3,CMan and woman arrested over 'murder
OL,4,Cplot' after anti-terror raid
OL,6,F"Following the discovery of
OL,7,Fpotentially suspicious items at the
OL,8,Fresidential address, the Explosive
OL,9,FOrdnance Disposal Unit (EOD) have been
OL,10,Fcalled to provide expert advice as a
OL,11,Fprecautionary measure.
OL,13,F"The fire service has also been in
OL,14,Fattendance."
OL,16,FHumberside Police said it was stepping
OL,17,Fup patrols following the arrests.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/3
